text: Aleksandr Yevdokimov (born 5 April 1947) is a Soviet equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1968 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1947 births Category:Living people Category:Soviet male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of the Soviet Union Category:Equestrians at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:People from Mary, Turkmenistan
